metadata.name: Game Over #1/50
metadata.description: 'Game Over' is not just an art piece, it's a message that speaks to our everyday lives. When it seems like the game of life is over, we mustn't give up. Instead, we must keep pushing and fighting. It's easy to get discouraged and feel like giving up, but remember that the game isn't really over until you say it is. So let's keep going, keep creating, and keep pushing ourselves to achieve greatness. Together, we can make sure that the game is never truly over.
